            <span class="css-truncate css-truncate-target"><a class="js-navigation-open" title="contributing.md" id="cc4aac3e9be04e0413c9520f223b493c-1952d086e69baabba16457f7b72046545c20cef5" href="/sindresorhus/awesome-scifi/blob/master/contributing.md">contributing.md</a></span>
