<p>This book is insidiously horrifying in its applicability, more so than <em>1984</em> or <em>Fahrenheit 451</em>. <a href="https://abetterkuwait.files.wordpress.com/2011/08/orwell-huxley.jpg" rel="nofollow">Here's a comic</a> that sums up the difference. Well worth the read. - <a href="https://github.com/RichardLitt">@RichardLitt</a></p>
