<h4><a id="user-content-fahrenheit-451-1953-by-ray-bradbury-40--" class="anchor" aria-hidden="true" href="#fahrenheit-451-1953-by-ray-bradbury-40--"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17470674-fahrenheit-451" rel="nofollow">Fahrenheit 451</a> (1953) <em>by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Bradbury" rel="nofollow">Ray Bradbury</a></em> [4.0] <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="star2" fallback-src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f31f.png">ðŸŒŸ</g-emoji> <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="fire" fallback-src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f525.png">ðŸ”¥</g-emoji></h4>
