<p>Now, in celebration of the week-long, once-in-a-decade rite of Apert, the fraas and suurs prepare to venture beyond the concentâ€™s gatesâ€”at the same time opening them wide to welcome the curious â€œextrasâ€ in. During his first Apert as a fraa, Erasmas eagerly anticipates reconnecting with the landmarks and family he hasnâ€™t seen since he was â€œcollected.â€ But before the week is out, both the existence he abandoned and the one he embraced will stand poised on the brink of cataclysmic change.</p>
