<p>Together this dynamic pair begin a journey through space aided by quotes from <em>The Hitchhikerâ€™s Guide</em> (â€œA towel is about the most massively useful thing an interstellar hitchhiker can haveâ€) and a galaxy-full of fellow travelers: Zaphod Beeblebroxâ€”the two-headed, three-armed ex-hippie and totally out-to-lunch president of the galaxy; Trillian, Zaphodâ€™s girlfriend (formally Tricia McMillan), whom Arthur tried to pick up at a cocktail party once upon a time zone; Marvin, a paranoid, brilliant, and chronically depressed robot; Veet Voojagig, a former graduate student who is obsessed with the disappearance of all the ballpoint pens he bought over the years.</p>
