<p>Categories: <code>anime</code> <code>dystopia</code> <code>thriller</code></p>
<p>One of the first mainstream anime movies. Psychologically horrifying in more than a few ways. - <a href="https://github.com/RichardLitt">@RichardLitt</a></p>
