<p><g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="+1" fallback-src="https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f44d.png">ðŸ‘</g-emoji> I liked it. Very original. - <a href="https://github.com/sindresorhus">@sindresorhus</a></p>
